    <main>
        <section class="content">
            <h1>About Us</h1>
            <h4>Here to help you learn about brewskies, in hopes of helping people drink more Responsibility!</h4>
            <br>
            <h1>Our Mission</h1>
            <p>Have you ever been curious about the world of beer but not quite sure where to start? Tired of the same 
                stuff? Look no further! This collection of beers offers a great opportunity to explore and discover 
                new brews. </p>
            <p>At Brewski Buddy, Not only will you learn about the different types of beers, but we'll also share 
                some tips on how to enjoy them responsibly. After all, drinking beer can be a fun and social activity 
                when done in moderation. We encourage you to savor each beer, taking note of its unique characteristics
                and flavors, and experiment with pairing them with different foods.</p>
            <p>Whether you're enjoying a cold brew on a sunny day or kicking back with friends on a Friday night, we 
                hope this selection of beers helps you appreciate the art and science behind brewing, all while having 
                a good time.</p>
            <h1>Our Values</h1>
            <ul>
                <li>Bold: both in beer and our approach to business. We're not afraid to take risks, try new things,
                    and push the boundaries of traditional brewing techniques.</li>
                <li>Responsibility: We believe that beer can be enjoyed in moderation and as part of a balanced 
                    lifestyle, but we also recognize the dangers of excessive drinking.
                </li>
                <li>Education: We're constantly learning about new brewing techniques, ingredients, and flavor 
                    profiles, and we love to share that knowledge with our customers.
                </li>
                <li>Wisdom: Wisdom is about more than just knowledge; it's also about using that knowledge to make 
                    wise choices.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </main>

